item.how_to_find_us: I'll wear my tiara and wait for everyone at the restrooms near the train bridge...
item.why: They don't call me the Canal Queen for nothing! I thought about hosting this months walk at a different spot, but then I figured why mess with success? I've had a few requests to do it again from people who went and people who missed it, so let's go!
